title: Yuanqi Vegetarian
description: Vegan Yuanqi Vegetarian Restaurant is located near the junction of Altay Road and Xinyi Road. Walk about 200 meters north from the junction. On the left side of the road stands a big hotel with two buildings. Restaurant is located 50 meters inside a little alley between A and B wings. Closed on Tuesdays. Chinese name: 缘起素食坊. Address: 新疆乌鲁木齐市阿勒泰路2号大修厂QQ公寓大门内走100米.
streetAddress: Inside QQ Condo, Daxiuchang, 2# Aletai Rd.
